<article class="config-card">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <p class="panel-kicker">Tratamento</p>
      <h3>Limpeza e reprocessamento</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="config-module-intro">
    <strong>Recuperacao orientada por sinais de qualidade</strong>
    <p>Analise candidatos, limpe filas e execute o reprocesso imediato com base nas configuracoes definidas.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="stats-grid" id="maintenanceInsights"></div>

  <div class="button-row">
    <button id="maintenancePreview" class="ghost-button" type="button">Analisar fila</button>
    <button id="maintenanceClear" class="ghost-button danger-button" type="button">Limpar e voltar para pendente</button>
    <button id="maintenanceReprocess" class="primary-button" type="button">Limpar e reprocessar agora</button>
  </div>

  <p class="config-note" id="maintenanceFeedback">Aguardando analise.</p>
  <div id="maintenanceCandidates" class="stack-list"></div>
</article>

<article class="config-card">
  <div class="section-head">
    <div>
      <p class="panel-kicker">Saneamento textual</p>
      <h3>Corrigir textos ja indexados</h3>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="config-module-intro">
    <strong>Ajuste fino do texto salvo</strong>
    <p>Gere preview e aplique correcoes de legibilidade sobre textos salvos sem baixar o PDF novamente.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="button-row">
    <button id="textCleanupPreview" class="ghost-button" type="button">Gerar preview</button>
    <button id="textCleanupRun" class="primary-button" type="button">Aplicar limpeza no texto salvo</button>
  </div>

  <p class="config-note" id="textCleanupFeedback">Aguardando preview.</p>
  <div id="textCleanupCandidates" class="stack-list"></div>
</article>
